<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<base href="&mvte:global:basehref;">
	<title>Sinister Diesel Performance Parts | Powerstroke, Duramax &amp; Cummins</title>
	<meta name="description" content="Shop performance parts for Ford Powerstroke, Chevy Duramax and Dodge Cummins trucks, with live fitment guidance, installation resources and US-based support.">
	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if>
	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
	<mvt:comment>
		Sinister Diesel Homepage. Live SFNT template migrated to the approved
		Revamp V2 design. Uses the same global layer as header/footer/nav:
		- cssui-global-header-v2.mvt
		- cssui-mega-menu-v2.mvt
		- cssui-search-console-v2.mvt
		- sd2-v2-garage-selector.mvt
		- sd2-v2-cart-drawer.mvt
		- cssui-global-footer-v2.mvt
		Canonical partial references:
		- sd2-v2-perfstrip.mvt
		- sd2-v2-product-card.mvt
		- sd2-v2-build-story.mvt
	</mvt:comment>
</head>
<body>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

	<mvt:comment>Load the live New Products category directly from Miva for the homepage.</mvt:comment>
	<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_category_loaded" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Category_Load_Code('1209456_new_products', l.settings:sd2_home_category)" />
	<mvt:if expr="l.sd2_home_category_loaded">
		<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_product_count" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Runtime_ProductList_Load_Offset_Category(l.settings:sd2_home_category:id, 0, 6, l.settings:sd2_home_next_offset, l.settings:sd2_home_products)" />
		<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_prices_ready" file="g.Module_Feature_TUI_UT" value="CommonComponentFields_Initialize_Product_Discounts_Runtime(l.settings:sd2_home_products, l.sd2_home_product_count)" />
		<mvt:do name="l.settings:sd2_home_category_url" file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" value="Store_Category_URL(l.settings:sd2_home_category, NULL)" />
		<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_image_type_loaded" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="ImageType_Load_Code('main', l.settings:sd2_home_image_type)" />
	</mvt:if>

<main class="sd2-v2-home" data-v2-home>
	<div class="sd2-v2-home-intro" aria-hidden="true"><span>Sinister Diesel</span></div>
	<section class="sd2-v2-home-hero" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-home-hero-title">
		<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__shell">
			<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__frame">
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__copy sd2-reveal sd2-reveal--right" data-reveal="fade-right">
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Performance You Control</p>
					<h1 class="sd2-v2-home-hero__title" id="sd2-v2-home-hero-title">Built to pull harder.<br>Run cooler.<br>Go farther.</h1>
					<p class="sd2-body">Fitment-first diesel performance for Powerstroke, Duramax, and Cummins. Real parts, live pricing, and a build path shaped around your truck.</p>
					<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__actions">
						<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Build Around My Truck</button>
						<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline sd2-hero-platform-cta" href="#sd2-v2-platforms-title"><span>Explore Platforms</span></a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__media sd2-depth-scene" aria-label="Sinister Diesel performance truck">
					<img class="sd2-depth-layer" data-sd2-depth="-0.1" src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="Sinister Diesel performance truck">
					<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__telemetry sd2-depth-layer sd2-reveal sd2-reveal--left" data-sd2-depth="0.18" data-reveal="fade-left">
						<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__telemetry-head"><span>Live Build System</span><i aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
						<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__telemetry-core"><span>Platform coverage</span><strong>3</strong><small>Powerstroke / Duramax / Cummins</small></div>
						<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__telemetry-row"><span>Catalog</span><strong>Live Miva data</strong></div>
						<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__telemetry-row"><span>Fitment</span><strong>Garage ready</strong></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-hero__factline sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
					<span>01 &nbsp; MADE AND TESTED IN THE USA</span>
					<span>02 &nbsp; SINCE 2009</span>
					<span>03 &nbsp; FITMENT-FIRST SHOPPING</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v2-perfstrip" aria-label="Sinister Diesel proof points">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__grid sd2-stagger" data-reveal="fade-up">
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value" data-v2-count-to="2009">2009</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">SINCE</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">USA</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">DESIGNED AND TESTED</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">FORD</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">POWERSTROKE</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">GM</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">DURAMAX</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__item"><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__value">RAM</span><span class="sd2-v2-perfstrip__label">CUMMINS</span></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v4-power-journey" data-v4-power-journey aria-labelledby="sd2-v4-power-title">
		<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__sticky">
			<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__grid" role="presentation"></div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__head"><span>Performance, visualized</span><span data-v4-scene-index>01 / 03</span></div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__copy">
				<article class="sd2-v4-power-chapter is-active" data-v4-chapter>
					<p>Airflow</p><h2 id="sd2-v4-power-title">Let it<br>breathe.</h2><span>Intakes, charge pipes, and intercoolers organized around your truck.</span>
				</article>
				<article class="sd2-v4-power-chapter" data-v4-chapter>
					<p>Cooling</p><h2>Hold the<br>line.</h2><span>Cooling and monitoring parts for builds that work under load.</span>
				</article>
				<article class="sd2-v4-power-chapter" data-v4-chapter>
					<p>Control</p><h2>Build with<br>intent.</h2><span>Tuners, sensors, and supporting parts in one connected catalog.</span>
				</article>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-turbine" role="presentation">
				<div class="sd2-v4-turbine__orbit"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
				<svg class="sd2-v4-turbine__truck" viewBox="0 0 720 460" role="presentation" focusable="false">
					<defs>
						<linearGradient id="sd2-truck-body" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#27354b"/><stop offset=".42" stop-color="#0c1422"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#020711"/></linearGradient>
						<linearGradient id="sd2-truck-side" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop stop-color="#182945"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#050912"/></linearGradient>
						<linearGradient id="sd2-truck-glass" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop stop-color="#315b97"/><stop offset=".5" stop-color="#0d213e"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#050a14"/></linearGradient>
						<radialGradient id="sd2-truck-wheel"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#376ff4"/><stop offset=".18" stop-color="#0a1120"/><stop offset=".58" stop-color="#131a25"/><stop offset=".64" stop-color="#030508"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#10151d"/></radialGradient>
						<filter id="sd2-truck-glow" x="-80%" y="-80%" width="260%" height="260%"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="12"/></filter>
					</defs>
					<ellipse cx="369" cy="381" rx="264" ry="25" fill="#1d5eff" opacity=".33" filter="url(#sd2-truck-glow)"/>
					<path d="M92 260 153 154l87-45h218l73 80 119 31 24 84-33 31H119l-50-29Z" fill="url(#sd2-truck-body)" stroke="#4778e8" stroke-width="3"/>
					<path d="m239 119 42-45h151l91 112-276-2Z" fill="url(#sd2-truck-side)" stroke="#365584" stroke-width="3"/>
					<path d="m287 87-34 86h107V86Zm89-1v87h125l-70-87Z" fill="url(#sd2-truck-glass)" stroke="#75a1ff" stroke-opacity=".45" stroke-width="3"/>
					<path d="M240 185h293l112 30-17 96H223Z" fill="url(#sd2-truck-side)" stroke="#27436d" stroke-width="3"/>
					<path d="M91 260h141v72H111l-43-27Z" fill="#050912" stroke="#4168b8" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M101 272h117v12H96Zm-6 20h123v10H91Zm5 18h118v9H105Z" fill="#234f9e"/>
					<path d="M72 251h45l17 26H81Z" fill="#e9f4ff"/><path d="M75 256h52" stroke="#2367ff" stroke-width="8"/>
					<path d="M530 215h108l23 78-22 18H528Z" fill="#0a101b" stroke="#31548a" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M543 232h96" stroke="#477eff" stroke-width="5" opacity=".8"/>
					<path d="M238 200v108m145-111v111m145-98v101" stroke="#34527c" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M258 222h93m54 0h94" stroke="#5676a7" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					<path d="M205 321h364" stroke="#3470ff" stroke-width="7" opacity=".9"/>
					<g><circle cx="199" cy="330" r="78" fill="#020409" stroke="#1d2a3e" stroke-width="9"/><circle cx="199" cy="330" r="48" fill="url(#sd2-truck-wheel)" stroke="#4269ae" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M199 291v78m-39-39h78m-67-28 56 56m0-56-56 56" stroke="#7997ca" stroke-width="5"/></g>
					<g><circle cx="558" cy="330" r="78" fill="#020409" stroke="#1d2a3e" stroke-width="9"/><circle cx="558" cy="330" r="48" fill="url(#sd2-truck-wheel)" stroke="#4269ae" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M558 291v78m-39-39h78m-67-28 56 56m0-56-56 56" stroke="#7997ca" stroke-width="5"/></g>
					<path d="M149 133h93v12h-99Zm-32 184h524" stroke="#6f9fff" stroke-width="4" opacity=".7"/>
				</svg>
				<div class="sd2-v4-turbine__core"><span>Truck telemetry</span><strong data-v4-signal>Airflow</strong><small>Live build path</small></div>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__telemetry" aria-label="Build system status">
				<div><span>Fitment</span><strong>Garage linked</strong></div><div><span>Inventory</span><strong>Live from Miva</strong></div><div><span>Support</span><strong>Human backed</strong></div>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-power-journey__rail" role="presentation"><i></i></div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v3-process" aria-labelledby="sd2-v3-process-title" data-sd2-story>
		<div class="sd2-v3-process__intro">
			<p class="sd2-eyebrow">The Sinister Build Path</p>
			<h2 id="sd2-v3-process-title">From your truck<br>to the right parts.</h2>
			<p>One connected path from fitment to checkout, backed by the live Sinister Diesel catalog.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="sd2-v3-process__steps">
			<article class="sd2-v3-process-card" data-sd2-story-step>
				<span class="sd2-v3-process-card__number">01</span>
				<div><p class="sd2-kicker">Start with fitment</p><h3>Save your truck</h3><p>Choose your platform and engine once. Garage carries that context through the storefront.</p></div>
				<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Add Your Truck</button>
			</article>
			<article class="sd2-v3-process-card" data-sd2-story-step>
				<span class="sd2-v3-process-card__number">02</span>
				<div><p class="sd2-kicker">Build with confidence</p><h3>Explore live inventory</h3><p>Browse current products, pricing, availability, and platform-specific categories directly from Miva.</p></div>
				<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="/new-products.html">Shop New Products</a>
			</article>
			<article class="sd2-v3-process-card" data-sd2-story-step>
				<span class="sd2-v3-process-card__number">03</span>
				<div><p class="sd2-kicker">Finish the build</p><h3>Get real support</h3><p>Use product guidance, installation resources, and the Sinister Diesel support team when you need them.</p></div>
				<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="/help-center.html">Open Help Center</a>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v5-truck-lab" data-v5-truck-lab aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-platforms-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<header class="sd2-v5-truck-lab__head sd2-reveal">
				<div><p class="sd2-eyebrow">The Truck Lab</p><h2 id="sd2-v2-platforms-title">Three platforms.<br>One moving playground.</h2></div>
				<p>Rotate through the trucks, inspect each build path, and enter the live Miva catalog from the platform that is actually in your driveway.</p>
			</header>

			<div class="sd2-v5-truck-lab__shell">
				<div class="sd2-v5-truck-stage" data-v5-truck-stage tabindex="0" role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Diesel truck platforms">
					<article class="sd2-v5-truck is-active" data-v5-truck="powerstroke" aria-hidden="false">
						<a class="sd2-v5-truck__visual" href="/ford-powerstroke-powerstroke-diesel-truck-parts-online.html" tabindex="0">
							<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%201.png" alt="Ford Super Duty representing the Powerstroke catalog">
							<span class="sd2-v5-truck__scan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</a>
						<div class="sd2-v5-truck__hud">
							<p><span>01</span> Powerstroke</p><h3>Blue Oval.<br>Build it your way.</h3>
							<div class="sd2-v5-truck__readout"><span>Platform</span><strong>Ford Super Duty</strong><span>Catalog</span><strong>Live Miva Parts</strong></div>
							<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--light" href="/ford-powerstroke-powerstroke-diesel-truck-parts-online.html">Enter Powerstroke</a>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="sd2-v5-truck is-next" data-v5-truck="duramax" aria-hidden="true">
						<a class="sd2-v5-truck__visual" href="/shop-gm-duramax-diesel-parts-sinister-diesel.html" tabindex="-1">
							<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="GM heavy-duty pickup representing the Duramax catalog">
							<span class="sd2-v5-truck__scan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</a>
						<div class="sd2-v5-truck__hud">
							<p><span>02</span> Duramax</p><h3>Heavy duty.<br>Dialed in.</h3>
							<div class="sd2-v5-truck__readout"><span>Platform</span><strong>GM Heavy Duty</strong><span>Catalog</span><strong>Live Miva Parts</strong></div>
							<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--light" href="/shop-gm-duramax-diesel-parts-sinister-diesel.html" tabindex="-1">Enter Duramax</a>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="sd2-v5-truck is-prev" data-v5-truck="cummins" aria-hidden="true">
						<a class="sd2-v5-truck__visual" href="/dodge-cummins-diesel-performance-parts-sinister-diesel.html" tabindex="-1">
							<img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%202.png" alt="Ram heavy-duty pickup representing the Cummins catalog">
							<span class="sd2-v5-truck__scan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</a>
						<div class="sd2-v5-truck__hud">
							<p><span>03</span> Cummins</p><h3>Inline six.<br>All business.</h3>
							<div class="sd2-v5-truck__readout"><span>Platform</span><strong>Ram Heavy Duty</strong><span>Catalog</span><strong>Live Miva Parts</strong></div>
							<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--light" href="/dodge-cummins-diesel-performance-parts-sinister-diesel.html" tabindex="-1">Enter Cummins</a>
						</div>
					</article>
				</div>

				<div class="sd2-v5-truck-controls">
					<button type="button" data-v5-truck-prev aria-label="Previous truck">&#8592;</button>
					<div role="tablist" aria-label="Choose a truck platform">
						<button type="button" role="tab" data-v5-truck-select="powerstroke" aria-selected="true"><i>01</i> Powerstroke</button>
						<button type="button" role="tab" data-v5-truck-select="duramax" aria-selected="false"><i>02</i> Duramax</button>
						<button type="button" role="tab" data-v5-truck-select="cummins" aria-selected="false"><i>03</i> Cummins</button>
					</div>
					<button type="button" data-v5-truck-next aria-label="Next truck">&#8594;</button>
				</div>
				<p class="sd2-v5-truck-lab__hint"><span></span> Drag the stage or use arrow keys</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section--tight sd2-v2-home-garage" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-garage-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-garage-prompt sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
				<div>
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">My Garage</p>
					<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-garage-title">Save your truck before you shop.</h2>
					<p class="sd2-body">Your saved vehicle stays available while you browse categories, compare products, and manage your account.</p>
				</div>
				<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Add Your Truck</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-v4-build-console" data-v4-build-console aria-labelledby="sd2-v4-build-console-title">
		<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__intro">
			<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Choose Your Intent</p>
			<h2 id="sd2-v4-build-console-title">What does your truck need to do?</h2>
			<p>Switch the build mode, then save your truck so the storefront can keep your platform close.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__machine">
			<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__switch" role="tablist" aria-label="Build mode">
				<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" data-v4-mode="daily">Daily</button>
				<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-v4-mode="tow">Tow</button>
				<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-v4-mode="performance">Performance</button>
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__display">
				<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__dial" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><span data-v4-mode-code>01</span></div>
				<div class="sd2-v4-build-console__panels">
					<article class="is-active" data-v4-mode-panel="daily"><span>Mode 01</span><h3>Daily-driver balance.</h3><p>Start with maintenance, filtration, monitoring, and platform-correct essentials.</p></article>
					<article data-v4-mode-panel="tow"><span>Mode 02</span><h3>Confidence under load.</h3><p>Explore cooling, airflow, transmission, and monitoring paths for towing priorities.</p></article>
					<article data-v4-mode-panel="performance"><span>Mode 03</span><h3>Build the system.</h3><p>Connect airflow, fuel, tuning, and supporting parts instead of treating upgrades in isolation.</p></article>
				</div>
			</div>
			<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" type="button" data-v2-garage-toggle>Match My Truck</button>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-products sd2-v4-product-runway" data-v4-product-runway aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-products-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-section-head sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
				<p class="sd2-eyebrow">New Products</p>
				<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-products-title">Fresh parts, pricing, and availability from the live catalog.</h2>
			</div>
			<mvt:if expr="miva_array_elements(l.settings:sd2_home_products) GT 0">
				<div class="sd2-v2-product-grid sd2-stagger">
					<mvt:foreach iterator="product" array="sd2_home_products">
						<mvt:assign name="l.settings:sd2_home_image" value="NULL" />
						<mvt:assign name="l.settings:sd2_home_product_image" value="NULL" />
						<mvt:do name="l.settings:sd2_home_product_url" file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" value="Store_Product_URL(l.settings:product, NULL)" />
						<mvt:if expr="l.sd2_home_image_type_loaded">
							<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_product_image_loaded" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="ProductImage_Load_Type(l.settings:product:id, 1, l.settings:sd2_home_product_image)" />
							<mvt:if expr="l.sd2_home_product_image_loaded">
								<mvt:do name="l.sd2_home_image_loaded" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Image_Load_ID(l.settings:sd2_home_product_image:image_id, l.settings:sd2_home_image)" />
							</mvt:if>
						</mvt:if>
						<article class="sd2-card sd2-v2-product-card sd2-tilt">
							<a class="sd2-v2-product-card__media" href="&mvte:sd2_home_product_url;">
								<mvt:if expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:sd2_home_image:image">
									<img src="&mvte:sd2_home_image:image;" alt="&mvte:product:name;" loading="lazy">
								<mvt:elseif expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:product:thumbnail">
									<img src="&mvte:product:thumbnail;" alt="&mvte:product:name;" loading="lazy">
								<mvt:else>
									<span class="sd2-v2-product-card__image-fallback" aria-hidden="true">SD</span>
								</mvt:if>
							</a>
							<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__body">
								<p class="sd2-v2-product-card__platform">SKU &mvte:product:code;</p>
								<h3 class="sd2-v2-product-card__title"><a href="&mvte:sd2_home_product_url;">&mvte:product:name;</a></h3>
								<div class="sd2-v2-product-card__foot">
									<div class="sd2-v2-price">
										<span class="sd2-v2-price__label">Price</span>
										<div class="sd2-v2-price__row">
											<mvt:if expr="l.settings:product:base_price GT l.settings:product:price"><span class="sd2-v2-price__was"><s>&mvt:product:formatted_base_price;</s></span></mvt:if>
											<span class="sd2-v2-price__current">&mvt:product:formatted_price;</span>
										</div>
									</div>
									<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--secondary sd2-btn--compact" href="&mvte:sd2_home_product_url;">View Part</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</article>
					</mvt:foreach>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-products__all sd2-reveal"><a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="&mvte:sd2_home_category_url;">View All New Products</a></div>
			<mvt:else>
				<div class="sd2-v2-home-products__empty"><p>New products are being prepared now.</p><a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary" href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/954746_ford_powerstroke">Shop Performance Parts</a></div>
			</mvt:if>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-build" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-build-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<article class="sd2-v2-build-story sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
				<div class="sd2-v2-build-story__media sd2-tilt sd2-depth-scene"><img class="sd2-depth-layer" data-sd2-depth="-0.06" src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="Diesel tow-rig performance build"></div>
				<div class="sd2-v2-build-story__body">
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Build Blueprint</p>
					<h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-build-title">Plan the system before the parts.</h2>
					<p class="sd2-body">Start with your truck, choose how it works, then build through cooling, airflow, filtration, and monitoring without losing the thread.</p>
					<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="#sd2-v2-platforms-title">Choose Your Platform</a>
				</div>
				<aside class="sd2-v2-build-story__specs" aria-label="Build specifications">
					<div><span>01</span><strong>Save Your Truck</strong></div>
					<div><span>02</span><strong>Choose a Use Case</strong></div>
					<div><span>03</span><strong>Verify Fitment</strong></div>
				</aside>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section--tight sd2-v2-home-trust" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-trust-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-section-head sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up"><p class="sd2-eyebrow">Proof Points</p><h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-trust-title">Specific reasons to trust the build.</h2></div>
			<div class="sd2-v2-trust-grid sd2-stagger">
				<div><strong>Diesel Focus</strong><span>Built around Powerstroke, Duramax, Cummins, and the systems that support them.</span></div>
				<div><strong>Built for the Shop</strong><span>Clear fitment paths help move from truck to compatible parts with less guesswork.</span></div>
				<div><strong>Real Build Support</strong><span>Product, fitment, order, and installation questions connect to the support team.</span></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="sd2-section sd2-v2-home-content" aria-labelledby="sd2-v2-content-title">
		<div class="sd2-wrap">
			<div class="sd2-v2-content-teaser sd2-reveal" data-reveal="fade-up">
				<div><p class="sd2-eyebrow">Learn Before You Buy</p><h2 class="sd2-heading-lg" id="sd2-v2-content-title">Guides, installs, and build notes belong beside the parts.</h2></div>
				<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--outline" href="&mvte:urls:NEWS:auto;">View Guides</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
